<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Event Cancelled: {{eventName}}</title>
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8d7da; 
      margin: 0; 
      padding: 0; 
    }
    .container { 
      max-width: 600px; 
      margin: 40px auto; 
      background: #fff; 
      border: 1px solid #f5c6cb; 
      border-radius: 8px; 
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header { 
      background-color: #dc3545; 
      color: #fff; 
      padding: 20px; 
      text-align: center; 
    }
    .header h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: normal;
    }
    .content { 
      padding: 30px 20px;
      font-size: 16px; 
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .button-container {
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .btn {
      background-color: #dc3545;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 16px;
      display: inline-block;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease-in-out;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #c82333;
    }
    .footer { 
      background-color: #f1f1f1;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #721c24;
      border-top: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Event Cancelled</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>We regret to inform you that the event <strong>{{eventName}}</strong> you registered for has been cancelled.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions, please contact the event organizers.</p>
      <div class="button-container">
        <a class="btn" href="{{url}}" target="_blank">View Event Details</a>
      </div>
      <p>If the button does not work, copy and paste the URL below into your browser:</p>
      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #dc3545;">{{url}}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,<br/>PASA Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
